reviewText: what can I say- its Barak Obama- a time when dignity and intelligence was infused into the office.
Great Documentary!!! It highlighted some good key moments in his political career.

This was a total disappointment.  Nothing but a string of pasted videos of past speeches.  The overall quality of this DVD was very, very poor.  I'm an avid supporter and I wouldn't recommend this to anyone.

Your product was everything you advertise.  I will be re-ordering products of this kind again.  I have a President Obama Collection and this item will go very well with my collection.  Thank you again, a well satisfied customer.

I am an Obama supporter first of all. I purchased this because I wanted something for the history archive. Although it does contain a lot of his major speeches I felt that they also left a lot out. I was a little disappointed not to get a better feel for Obama the man, not just Obama the President and I think it could have been edited a little better. Still I am glad I purchased it, but will probably order some other documentaries to supplement it.
